Package: bGMYC4
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian GMYC Model for Species Delimitation (Development Version)
Version: 4.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Noah", "Reid", email = "noah.reid@gmail.com", role = c("aut"), comment = "Original author of bGMYC"),
    person("Dmitry", "Karabanov", email = "dk@ibiw.ru", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = "Maintainer of bGMYC4"),
    person("Qwen", "3.6", email = "qwen@alibabacloud.com", role = c("ctb"), comment = "Code modernization and R 4.x compatibility")
  )
Description: Implements a Bayesian version of the general mixed Yule-coalescent
    model for species delimitation introduced by Pons et al. (2006). It uses
    Markov Chain Monte Carlo simulation to evaluate the posterior distribution
    of the model and supports flexible prior specification on model parameters.
